Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的味噌湯是兩位的閨女做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望爸爸媽媽會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看起來就不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:47.76,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安 鷲尾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}媽媽 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇怪 我不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木 你在教室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且馬上就是晨會了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲尾 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位同學 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之輪銀同學 你遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:29.28,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛 很痛耶老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趕快就座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小銀 你今天怎麼遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}升上六年級總會有不少事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忘記帶課本了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的值日生是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}起立
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們能來這裡 都是託神樹大人的福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向神龕敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們該完成使命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還是第一次見到呢 原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神樹大人的結界？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.52,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs70\pos(394,200)\alpha&HFF&\t(0,300,0\alpha&F00&)}第{\r\blur2\fs70\alpha&HFF&\t(200,500,0\alpha&F00&)}一{\r\blur2\fs70\alpha&HFF&\t(400,700,0\alpha&F00&)}集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.52,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(0,300,0\alpha&F00&)\move(620,480,640,500,0,400)}鷲{\r\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(200,500,0\alpha&F00&)}尾{\r\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(400,700,0\alpha&F00&)}須{\r\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(600,900,0\alpha&F00&)}美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是神樹大人做出的結界內的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹海…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟聽到的一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好壯觀 全都是樹耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是大橋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概就是那個沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連接起這裡與牆壁外的橋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敵人會從那裡襲擊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好興奮 我們竟然成了勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之輪 這可不是說著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就是敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那傢伙跨過大橋 到達神樹大人身邊時
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界就會不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得由我們阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來完成使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒼茫天地中 森羅萬象拂吾身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明駐吾心 遵吾意願現世間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}獻吾之精魂 萬丈神力齊相助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}獻吾之精魂 承蒙聖力御外敵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的第一次實戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我們還沒有做配合訓練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為敵人出現的時間比神諭提及的更早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過應該沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小心應付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 幹掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們都站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:08:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好寬敞 跟訓練時完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想不到這裡原本是城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太奇妙了 鷲尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從另一側來襲的傢伙 Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擊退敵人所花的時間越長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原本的世界就會受到越大的負面影響
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}速戰速決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兩位！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看我一斧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想起來這個可以當盾用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟強烈颱風一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲尾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種敵人要怎麼對付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的弓箭傷害不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之輪力氣不小 但難以近身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木連我都不知道怎麼應付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到底該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行動起來就危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之輪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彈性好強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然全喝下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是獲得了神力的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把水喝乾不費吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 你好厲害 有味道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一開始是汽水 喝著喝著變成烏龍茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽起來並不好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在要緊的是Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那傢伙很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分身神靈太多了 肯定離出口不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但剛才的攻擊沒有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但不快點 它就要跑出大橋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它要是跑出去 就沒辦法擊退了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拿出鬥志再戰一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我突然有個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它發現我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}轉來我們這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得抓緊時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}展開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這把長槍能變化成盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園子真是萬能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}頂著盾牌前進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木 撐得住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者要看鬥志 把它頂回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 鷲尾也跟著喊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一二 一二 一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲尾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好難瞄準
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 我把你甩過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之輪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嚐到厲害了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鎮魂之儀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我狠狠地給它吃了一頓斧頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多虧有你 儀式開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平息下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擊退…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來我們不會直接回學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟了 還穿著室內鞋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛才拍到樹海了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 照片不是樹海了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來是拍不下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 鷲尾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}須美？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}須美助？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是險勝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果只有我一個人 就輸定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.57,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord0\fs30\1c&H545454&\frx356\fry6\frz5.832\pos(250,296)}【沒有朋友】如何與人交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.57,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&H545454&\frz5.832\pos(272,398)\frx356\fry2}「沒有朋友…」這個煩惱很讓人難受吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.57,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&H545454&\frx356\fry2\pos(308,600)\frz6.678}我來教你幾招交朋友的訣竅吧♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.57,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷粗黑\bord2\b0\fs30\1c&H6938F2&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frx356\fry2\frz6.678\pos(344,646)}3{\shad2\bord2\1c&HC6DAD9&\3c&H3B4C4F&\4c&H3B4C4F&}大妙招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天也跟各位同學說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這三位同學肩負著神樹大人指派的重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以她們會像昨天那樣 突然從教室消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到時候不要慌張慌亂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}靜下心來 默默為她們三個加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}同學們還是要以平日的課業為重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}使命很辛苦嗎 受了傷很痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這可不能告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小氣鬼～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.07,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}告訴我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木 三之輪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以的話…我們去開個慶功宴…好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:18:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…我對平安迎來今天 感到由衷的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這美好的一天我宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神世紀298年 勇者初戰告捷慶功宴正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}祝在座的各位身體健康 學業有成 前途無量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.19,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太死板了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 須美助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我之前也好幾次想邀請你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但沒能說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以超開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是鷲尾第一次主動邀請我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}確實如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都還沒配合演練過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我們第一場戰鬥打得真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也很興奮 有好多想說的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是 想要和你們說說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以邀請了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我以前不是很信任你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}並不是說我討厭你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是我不習慣依賴他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}須美助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果…只有我一個人 肯定什麼都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為有你們在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能跟你們當朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們不是已經是了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好開心 我也好想和須美助當朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實我也不太會交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來須美助的想法跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好開心呀 須美助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼突然用須美助叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知不覺就幫你取了個綽號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你自己都沒自覺喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高興是高興啦 但我不太喜歡這個綽號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那鷲娜怎麼樣 很有偶像的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}更不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木也不喜歡「園琳琳」這種叫法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 當我沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想到了 你覺得「鷲鷲」怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就這樣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請多指教 鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 那你們就叫我銀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「三之輪」聽起來好見外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來慶祝交上朋友的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家一起去吃這裡超讚的冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}選擇焙茶‧可爾必思口味太對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三你的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}醬油蠶豆口味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什麼口味 不過看起來挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抹茶淡淡的苦編織出的口味 真是絕妙的搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼好吃的話 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事我是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃 這就是第一次配合工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用詞很會讓人想歪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早就想跟朋友做一次這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲鷲你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好開心呀
Comment: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,OP-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.58,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}キミを連れて駆け出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}誰も追いつけない場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:27.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}今こそ叶えようよ　あの日のやくそく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:42.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}片隅の幸せのつぼみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:45.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}銀色に輝いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:48.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}咲いたら見せてあげよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:53.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}見返したアルバムの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:56.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}その頃も今もそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:58.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}一緒に笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:04.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}南のほうから染まっていく季節
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:07.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}ただいまと言ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.29,0:23:10.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}きっとすぐに迎えに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:12.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}キミを連れて駆け出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}誰も追いつけない場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:20.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}今こそ叶えようよ　あの日のやくそく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:26.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}ねえ　ずっと待ってたよ　キミのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:32.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}おかえり　私をもう二度と置いてかないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.58,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}牽起你的手 邁開腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.19,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}去那片沒有人能夠追上的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:27.69,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}讓我們在這裡 實現那一天許下的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:42.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}吐露在角落裡的 一株幸福的花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:45.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}閃耀著銀露的光澤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:48.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}等它綻放 就讓我帶你來看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:53.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}翻來覆去過的這本相冊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:56.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}記錄著那個時候 還有今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:58.91,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}我們純真的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:04.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}南方吹來的春風 為世界染上了綠意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:07.29,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}記得說聲「我回來了」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.29,0:23:10.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}我一定三步並作兩步迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:12.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}牽起你的手 邁開腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}去那片沒有人能夠追上的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:20.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}讓我們在這裡 實現那一天許下的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:26.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}你知道嗎 我一直等待著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:32.81,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}歡迎回來 可不要再丟下我獨自啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神世紀298年 這是三位勇者交織成的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是被神明選中的少女們譜寫的童話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明選中的 總是天真無邪的少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而在大多數情況下 少女們的結局會是—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要舉例就是戰艦長門
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.23,0:24:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.79,0:24:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太古怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.90,0:24:19.95,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.05,0:24:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}玩真心話大冒險‧喜歡的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有園子在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.55,0:24:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回家前都是合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.34,0:24:26.31,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終點！
